{"tid":391392,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"Tom Ford冷艷\"夜行動物\"出沒","createTime":"2017-09-07T17:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T17:36:10.000Z","uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76417cc561d830884039397527db616ad87b3ea3","tid":391392,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/013509_5b34f431bb237345a50f79f0913f3bbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F013509_5b34f431bb237345a50f79f0913f3bbd.jpg&h=a4c41b12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/013513_952cc84d3731727e5099e5005fb707d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F013513_952cc84d3731727e5099e5005fb707d7.jpg&h=b3e7f517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTom Ford 2018 春夏時裝周回歸紐約，是繼2011春夏季在麥迪遜大道旗艦店和2016秋冬季舉辦的私密發布會後，首次在Big Apple進行大型的runway show。騷後在後台筆者問Tom Ford，究竟在紐約與倫敦舉辦時裝騷有何分別，眼前這位打扮一絲不苟的設計師說：「在紐約，有更多的人來睇show，除此之外沒有什麼分別。作為設計師，你會努力做到最好，並向自己施加壓力盡可能製作出最好的系列，無論在任何一個城市行show都一樣。但是，我恐怕來紐約看show和採訪的人會較倫敦的多。」<br />\n<br />\n我不知道各個時裝從業員是否偏重紐約，但我可以肯定的是，Tom Ford今晚的fashion show令紐約變得令人期待。大部分賓客準時到場，Poppy Delevingne和Man Repeller的Leandra Medine等名模fashionista一早到場，設計師好友Carine Roifeld更與一對子女結伴出席。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2xdYDXM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xdYDXM&d=WhmYtBF9Rnlk5MCaoV2acNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b82d3388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2xdYDXM</a>"}]}